nodes.text: Misty Lee (born April 22, 1976) is an American voice actress, comedian, and professional magician who voices Princess Leia Organa in Star Wars Battlefront and Star Wars Battlefront II. She is married to animation producer and comic-book author Paul Dini, with whom she lives in Los Angeles.
